'''Yoh Podd''' was a [[Jediboh Opera]] actor, part of [[Master Thespian]] [[Damien Tantrellius]]' [[Tantrellius Theatre Groupe]], and played the role of [[Mouchus]] in ''[[Two Jedi Men From Baronis]]''. He also had a thing for Damien's daughter [[Plum Tantrellius]] and, when she was kidnapped after a show, he insisted on joining the group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] who were trying to rescue her.

